  "prompt": "How can I search someone's follower list for a specific user on Instagram?",
  "response": "To search someone's follower list for a specific user on Instagram, follow these steps:\n\n### **1. Open Instagram and Go to the Profile:**\n   - Open the Instagram app or website and navigate to the profile of the person whose follower list you want to search.\n\n### **2. Access the Follower List:**\n   - Tap on the **Followers** count (e.g., \"X followers\") to open the list of followers.\n\n### **3. Use the Search Bar:**\n   - At the top of the follower list, you'll see a **Search Bar** labeled \"Search followers.\"\n   - Type the username or name of the specific user you're looking for.\n\n### **4. Review the Results:**\n   - Instagram will filter the follower list and display the users matching your search query.\n   - Scroll through the results to find the specific user.\n\n### **Notes:**\n   - If the account is private and you don\u2019t follow them, you won\u2019t be able to see their followers.\n   - The search feature only works if you\u2019re viewing the follower list of a public account or a private account that you follow.\n\nIf the person\u2019s account is private and you don\u2019t follow them, you won\u2019t have access to their follower list.",
